announcement.goals.bartender: See players that drink through walls!
announcement.goals.conductor: Use the master key to open up every door on the train!
announcement.goals.executioner: Become a killer once your target dies (to a non-killer). After killing your target, you gain 200 coins and a new random target is assigned.
announcement.goals.ghost: Killers cannot see your glowing outline, and sounds you make cannot be heard by others.
announcement.goals.jester: Find and co-operate with the Killers.
announcement.goals.noisemaker: Alert players of your location upon death.
announcement.goals.phantom: Turn invisible; but watch out for collisions.
announcement.goals.recaller: Teleport to anywhere on the train!
announcement.goals.voodoo: Choose another player to go down with you.
announcement.goals.vulture: Eat bodies to turn into a killer.
announcement.role.the_insane_damned_para: The Insane Damned Paranoid Killer Of Doom Death Destruction And Waffles
hud.voodoo.player_deaths_only: Voodoo deaths must be triggered by another player!
item.noellesroles.defense_vial.tooltip:
Right click on food/drink trays to use
Clears all poison applied to trays
Protects anyone who drinks a defensed drink one extra hit of life.
Invisible to other players.
item.noellesroles.delusion_vial.tooltip:
Right click on food/drink trays to use
Creates fakes poison, making the consumer of the poisoned item
think they are poisoned, but have no physical effect.
message.error.executioner.target_not_fou: Target player not found or already dead!
tip.master_key_invisible_count: Master Keys look like lockpicks with less than %s people.
